    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在残酷的世界中高举你的旗帜，这里唯有力量、钢铁与策略才能决定你的命运。率领传奇英雄，锻造不可阻挡的军队，在史诗级战役和大规模战场上粉碎敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >**《Lords And Legions》**是一款真正的中世纪奇幻战争游戏。以英雄为核心的战斗、宏大的战争场景、动态的战役模式，以及由你完全掌控的沙盒世界——在这里，你可以创造电影般的激烈冲突，或混乱无序的全面战争。战场，由你指挥。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/589050/extras/2be7e484d7cb2f47e415e3ef4773b4b9.poster.avif?t=1766086438\" width=800 height=700 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/589050/extras/2be7e484d7cb2f47e415e3ef4773b4b9.webm?t=1766086438\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/589050/extras/2be7e484d7cb2f47e415e3ef4773b4b9.mp4?t=1766086438\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚔️ <strong>战役模式</strong><br>在 <strong>Lords And Legions</strong> 中，每一场战役都是对你生存意志与征服欲望的考验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将从孤身一人开始——一位只带着少量金币的孤独英雄。<br>每一场战斗都是成长的机会。胜利会带来金币——你可以用这些金币组建军队、训练新兵，并为即将到来的战争做好准备。但随着你的军队不断壮大，敌人的力量与规模也会快速提升。每一支新的敌军都将比上一支更强、更庞大。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >若你战败，或许还能重整旗鼓——除非你选择了“硬核模式”。在硬核模式中，没有第二次机会。你做出的每一个决定、招募的每一名士兵、承担的每一次风险，都承载着生存或毁灭的代价。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你能在激烈的战斗中幸存，你将迎战各大阵营最强大的军队。击败他们，你的征服之路将继续，面对更强大、更危险的敌人。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/589050/extras/45a7ea9f9f521129b6f4d2c72f413970.poster.avif?t=1766086438\" width=800 height=700 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/589050/extras/45a7ea9f9f521129b6f4d2c72f413970.webm?t=1766086438\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/589050/extras/45a7ea9f9f521129b6f4d2c72f413970.mp4?t=1766086438\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 <strong>Lords And Legions</strong> 中，战役模式不仅是建立军队，更是缔造传奇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏰 <strong>沙盒模式</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 <strong>Lords And Legions</strong> 中，沙盒模式是一个完全属于你的世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以自由创造战场、设计战争，把脑海中的任何场景化为现实。你能堆起山丘、开凿峡谷、种植森林，甚至夷平整片大地——地形完全掌握在你手中。天气也可随心设置：宁静的夕阳、狂暴的风暴，或是笼罩黑雾的战场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/589050/extras/2754351e5177779e6a5d44e46d1ce60a.poster.avif?t=1766086438\" width=800 height=700 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/589050/extras/2754351e5177779e6a5d44e46d1ce60a.webm?t=1766086438\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/589050/extras/2754351e5177779e6a5d44e46d1ce60a.mp4?t=1766086438\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以随意摆放任何单位，数量不限。可以打造庞大的军团、小规模的冲突，或宏伟的攻城战。战斗的对手由你决定——帝国对抗战狂，亡灵对抗叛军，或者混合所有阵营，制造纯粹的混乱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论你渴望的是电影般的激烈对决、史诗级的最后防线，还是残酷血腥的自由混战，沙盒模式都能让你实现梦想中的战争。看着军队碰撞交锋，见证英雄的崛起与陨落，创造出难以忘怀的战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这里，没有既定规则。唯一的规则，就是你所制定的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/589050/extras/bdc988d3e9af0c54a147699f9d24046f.poster.avif?t=1766086438\" width=800 height=700 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/589050/extras/bdc988d3e9af0c54a147699f9d24046f.webm?t=1766086438\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/589050/extras/bdc988d3e9af0c54a147699f9d24046f.mp4?t=1766086438\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>这是一款由小型工作室倾注热情打造的作品。<br>我们始终欢迎来自玩家的反馈、想法和建议。<br>我们积极倾听社区的声音，并承诺将 <strong>《Lords And Legions》</strong> 打造成最佳的游戏体验。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/589050/extras/29297e463ce50a45cd84c6c0fba0bbc7.poster.avif?t=1766086438\" width=800 height=700 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/589050/extras/29297e463ce50a45cd84c6c0fba0bbc7.webm?t=1766086438\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/589050/extras/29297e463ce50a45cd84c6c0fba0bbc7.mp4?t=1766086438\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
